		<title type="html"><![CDATA[Updated v2.1.2.5]]></title>

		
		<content type="html" xml:base="https://forums.sandboxie.com/phpBB3/viewtopic.php?t=1983&amp;p=12396#p12396"><![CDATA[
Added enumeration of sandboxes from Sandboxie.ini.  An initial file selection dialog will be presented, then the path to your INI will be saved in sbie.ini along with the path to Start.exe.<br><br>The box parameter is now a fancy Combo Box!  It is a dropdown with your enumerated boxes, along with the new '__ask__' parameter and 'current' parameter.  The Combo Box also allows typing text input should you wish to use it.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.sandboxie.com/phpBB3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=846">wraithdu</a> — Mon Sep 17, 2007 12:05 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
